From: j0yen <jyen.tech@gmail.com>
Date: 2026-05-24
Subject: [PATCH 04/10] exit: notify agent_ns on task exit

Drop the per-NS live_tasks counter when a task exits so the end-of-NS
tracepoint fires at the right moment.

Signed-off-by: j0yen <jyen.tech@gmail.com>
---
 kernel/exit.c | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

--- a/kernel/exit.c
+++ b/kernel/exit.c
@@ -67,6 +67,7 @@
 #include <linux/io_uring.h>
 #include <linux/kprobes.h>
 #include <linux/rethook.h>
+#include <linux/agent_namespaces.h>

 #include <linux/uaccess.h>
 #include <asm/unistd.h>
@@ -869,6 +870,7 @@ void __noreturn do_exit(long code)

 	exit_signals(tsk);  /* sets PF_EXITING */

+	agent_ns_task_exit(tsk);
 	acct_update_integrals(tsk);
 	group_dead = atomic_dec_and_test(&tsk->signal->live);
 	if (group_dead) {
